  "name": "Morrison COU1 — FDA centrifugal pump hemolysis credibility assessment (Negative Control)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This negative-control package is intentionally clean: all 13 credibility factors are fully assessed with achievedLevel >= requiredLevel, provenance is complete, uncertainty quantification is documented, and the decision is Accepted. No weakener should fire on this package.",
